### Summary of ASX Announcement (Appendix 3C - Buy-back Notification):  

- **Buy-back Type**: Other buy-back (Nasdaq-listed Class A/B common stock repurchase; **no ASX-listed CDIs** included).  
- **Program Size**: Up to **US$1 billion** aggregate repurchase (mix of Class A/B shares).  
- **Recent Activity (03/07/2025)**:  
  - **Shares Repurchased**: 11,527 shares.  
  - **Total Consideration**: US$342,622.78 (average price ~US$29.71).  
  - **Price Range**: US$29.57 (low) to US$29.92 (high).  
- **Program Progress**:  
  - **Total Repurchased to Date**: ~US$692.2 million (69.2% of US$1 bn target).  
- **Broker**: Morgan Stanley.  
- **Purpose**: Enhance shareholder value.  

**No material impact on ASX-listed securities** (buy-back targets Nasdaq shares only).
